This is the README file for YAML::Syck, a fast, lightweight YAML loader
and dumper library.

Please type "perldoc YAML::Syck" after installation to see the
module usage information.

* Installation

YAML::Syck uses the standard perl module install process:

    cpansign -v         # optional; see SIGNATURE for details
    perl Makefile.PL
    make                # or 'nmake' on Win32
    make test
    make install

